{"tid":2368034,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情人節送咩好","createTime":"2021-01-15T22:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T12:49:40.000Z","uid":362382,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"669caa62ccc79563a516636089b56c8e03074024","tid":2368034,"uid":362382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T22:52:12.000Z","msg":"想送野俾男朋友。 利申真絲。<br />\n男朋友對我好好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前送過好多手作 ，又請過插畫家去畫本書，記錄咗大家拍拖點點滴滴喺本書仔。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果要煮餐飯，呢啲日日已經煮俾佢 怕冇驚喜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係今次諗唔到情人節送咩好俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bedb2eb7746a4b39798667d1a22e8800a1b1c5c","tid":2368034,"uid":308570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T22:53:41.000Z","msg":"綠帽"},{"pid":"c8db5c439ab2ca3105c1f24091bf7f865c473d64","tid":2368034,"uid":47941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T22:53:59.000Z","msg":"仲喺英國呀你？"},{"pid":"711645fc31994eb55a144605dc1da7e86f0f8061","tid":2368034,"uid":362382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bedb2eb7746a4b39798667d1a22e8800a1b1c5c","tid":2368034,"uid":308570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T22:53:41.000Z","msg":"綠帽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T22:54:12.000Z","msg":"唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da7f8ca16de5568736fdfb907836e816c8b7d06","tid":2368034,"uid":362382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8db5c439ab2ca3105c1f24091bf7f865c473d64","tid":2368034,"uid":47941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T22:53:59.000Z","msg":"仲喺英國呀你？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T22:54:25.000Z","msg":"係吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl